- Focused regressions already exist at `src/web/request_region.rs:474` (`run_cancelled_before_handler_returns_499`) and `src/web/request_region.rs:609` (`isolated_handler_cancelled_returns_499`).
- File-local formatting check passed: `rustfmt --edition 2024 --check src/web/request_region.rs src/web/response.rs`.

Validation attempts via `rch`:
